description:
Planet of the Apes Spectacular 01 (2013) (digital) (Minutemen-InnerPhDemons)


With time quickly running out, Alaya faces execution for her crimes against ape kind, while Sully begins to realize that the enemy of her enemy is not necessarily a friend either... It's Apes vs. Apes vs. Humans, as Daryl Gregory's epic continues in the PLANET OF THE APES SPECTACULAR!
